io.radanalytics.operator

Class SDKEntrypoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.radanalytics.operator.SDKEntrypoint

  • @ApplicationScoped
public class SDKEntrypoint
extends Object
    Entry point class that watches on StartupEvent and should bootstrap all the registered operators that are present on the class path. It scans the class path for those classes that have the Operator annotations on them or extends the AbstractOperator.
